<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>多模型协同编程助手</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1020;
      --card: #121931;
      --muted: #8fa2c9;
      --text: #eaf1ff;
      --accent: #5b8cff;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #18254f 0%, var(--bg) 46%);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .wrap {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 20px 56px;
    }
    h1 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 34px; }
    .sub { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 420px 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(18, 25, 49, 0.88);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      padding: 20px;
    }
    label { display: block; margin: 0 0 8px; font-weight: 700; }
    textarea, input {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      outline: none;
    }
    textarea { min-height: 160px; resize: vertical; }
    .mini { min-height: 120px; }
    .btn {
      margin-top: 14px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #5b8cff, #7a5cff);
      color: white;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .hint {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .stage {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .stage h3 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 17px; }
    .meta {
      color: #9db1d8;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    pre {
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
      background: rgba(6, 10, 23, 0.65);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
      overflow: auto;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .final {
      border: 1px solid rgba(91,140,255,0.3);
      background: rgba(91,140,255,0.08);
    }
    .loading { color: #ffd76a; margin: 10px 0; }
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>多模型协同编程助手</h1>
    <div class="sub">需求分析 → 架构设计 → 代码生成 → 测试设计 → Code Review → 文档集成</div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <label for="task">编程任务</label>
        <textarea id="task" placeholder="例如：帮我实现一个支持 JWT 登录、RBAC 权限控制、用户管理 CRUD 的 FastAPI 后端服务"></textarea>

        <label for="context" style="margin-top: 16px;">补充上下文</label>
        <textarea id="context" class="mini" placeholder="可以粘贴 PRD、错误日志、接口约束、数据库设计、技术栈要求等"></textarea>

        <button class="btn" id="submitBtn">开始协同编排</button>
        <div class="hint">
          说明：默认会按角色分工调用不同模型。你可以在后端 .env 中为 planner / architect / coder / tester / reviewer / doc_writer / integrator 配置不同 provider 和 model。
        </div>
        <div class="loading" id="loading"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div id="result"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/static/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
